Drive motors and ports - as viewed from back of robot

Control Hub

Motors
Leftfront: Port 0
Rightfront: Port 1
Lift: Port 2

Servos
Drone: Port 5


Expansion Hub

Motors
Leftback: Port 0
Rightback: Port 1
Climb: Port 2

Servos
Wrist: Port 5
Claw: Port 4

Digital In
LiftLimitSwitch: Port 0/1


Gamepad Controls List
Left Stick XY - Drive
Right Stick X -
Right Stick Y - Lift
Dpad UpDown - Climber
Dpad Left - Swap Wrist
Dpad Right - Swap Claw
Button X - Claw Grip
Button YAB - Lift Positions
Triggers LR - Strafe
Bumper L - Drone
Bumper R - Intake

Subsystem 1 - Drive
4x Motors with 16:1
    Drive - POV (Left Stick XY)
    Strafing - Slow (Triggers LR)

Subsystem 2 - Lift
1x Motor uP
    Set Points - Scoring & Intake (Buttons YAB)
    Small Adjustments (Right Stick Y)

Subsystem 3 - Claw
2x Servo
    Toggle Grip (Button X)
1x Position Servo
    Swap Order (Dpad Right)

Subsystem 4 - Wrist
1x Position Servo
    Set Points - Scoring & Intake (Dpad Left)

Subsystem 5 - Climber
1x Motor uP
    Extend (Dpad Up)
    Retract (Dpad Down)

Subsystem 6 - Drone
1x Small Position Servo
    Single Release - Time Locked (Bumper Left)

Subsystem 7 - Intake
Misc Things
    On/Off - Hold (Bumper Right)




